lead_paragraph: Brent Seabrook scored 1:02 into overtime after Artemi Panarin tied it late in the third period with his second goal of the game, and the Chicago Blackhawks beat the Winnipeg Jets 5-4 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Panarin Has 4 Points to Lift Blackhawks Over Jets 5-4 in OT
